{"tid":1009650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中線工程係梁振英貪污既結果","createTime":"2019-02-05T10:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T08:03:11.000Z","uid":74778,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee055a01d05e1e44979118d9be802aad229ab89e","tid":1009650,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/1529663140406747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F1529663140406747&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=b41f8161\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/1529663140406747</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1913078808731843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F1913078808731843&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=8a9abed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1913078808731843</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQKF1kv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQKF1kv.png&h=8eacb88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙中線所有問題嘅根源，可能都係一男子因素造成。<br />\n梁振英做咗行政長官5年，香港已經根基盡毀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n&gt;給梁振英的公開信<br />\n／8. 沒有申報就是沒有申報，況且，收了 UGL 錢的條件是否和特首職權有牴觸，不是由你來說。舉例，香港政府是港鐵公司的最大股東，而港鐵公司和UGL有商業往來，那麼你有沒有影響港鐵公司，使之增加或減少和UGL的合作？你也明白特首擁有廉署都無法制衡的權力，你有沒有透過委任或不委任某人當某職位，甚或宣佈或延緩政策，而使UGL得到好處呢？／<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/1529663140406747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F1529663140406747&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=11cedb6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/1529663140406747</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙中線 ／承建商禮頓／，CIMIC，UGL... 不用分得那麼細...<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1913078808731843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F1913078808731843&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=6da405fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1913078808731843</a><br />\n<br />\n圖： <a href=\"https://fb.com/maddog.hk/photos/a.198362040922194/298229877602076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fmaddog.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.198362040922194%2F298229877602076&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=889ca876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/maddog.hk/photos/a.198362040922194/298229877602076</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/907020282671039/posts/2267628833276837/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F907020282671039%2Fposts%2F2267628833276837%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=6956a4de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/907020282671039/posts/2267628833276837/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解林鄭月娥同鄭若驊放生佢？<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ac1946242138a71545bff1be787f4cfe704fce6","tid":1009650,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe1e43dae1dbfab69d7c15b17f5a7d7132a9b16","tid":1009650,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.